      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   srt-rec                .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiave di sort                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-osd-cod-rsm       to   srt-cod-rsm            .
           move      rf-osd-ide-dat       to   srt-ide-dat            .
           move      rf-osd-num-dst       to   srt-num-dst            .
           move      rf-osr-num-prt       to   srt-num-prt            .
           move      rf-osr-num-prg       to   srt-num-prg            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
